%hive
SELECT * FROM (
    SELECT vehicle_id,
        trip_id,
        datetime,
        velocity, 
        CASE WHEN ((LAG(velocity, 1, 0) OVER (PARTITION BY trip_id ORDER BY datetime) >= velocity)) THEN false ELSE true END AS is_accelerating,
        (velocity - LAG(velocity, 1, 0) OVER (PARTITION BY trip_id ORDER BY datetime)) AS acceleration
    FROM drive
    WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 
    AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
) t1 LIMIT 100

    WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500

) t1

paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT
    vehicle_id,
    trip_id,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM drive_sanitised WHERE previous_is_accelerating = true AND is_accelerating = false) AS ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM drive_sanitised WHERE is_accelerating = false) AS ft_sum_time_deaccel_val,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM drive_sanitised WHERE previous_is_accelerating = false AND is_accelerating = true) AS ft_count_vehicle_accel_val,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM drive_sanitised WHERE is_accelerating = true) AS ft_sum_time_accel_val
FROM drive_sanitised
GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id

paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT *
FROM (
    SELECT datetime,
    LAG(t1.is_accelerating, 1, false) OVER (ORDER BY t1.datetime) AS previous_is_accelerating,
    t1.is_accelerating AS is_accelerating
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, datetime,
            CASE WHEN ((LAG(velocity, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY datetime) >= velocity)) THEN false ELSE true END AS is_accelerating
        FROM drive
        WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 
        AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
    ) t1
) t2
WHERE t2.previous_is_accelerating = true
AND t2.is_accelerating = false

paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT *
FROM (
    SELECT datetime,
    LAG(t1.is_accelerating, 1, false) OVER (PARTITION BY t1.trip_id ORDER BY t1.datetime) AS previous_is_accelerating,
    t1.is_accelerating AS is_accelerating
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, datetime,
            CASE WHEN ((LAG(velocity, 1, 0) OVER (PARTITION BY trip_id ORDER BY datetime) >= velocity)) THEN false ELSE true END AS is_accelerating
        FROM drive
        WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 
        AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
    ) t1
) t2
WHERE t2.previous_is_accelerating = false
AND t2.is_accelerating = true

WHERE trip_id = (
  SELECT trip_id FROM drive WHERE velocity = (SELECT MIN(velocity) FROM drive)
)
ORDER BY datetime

SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, datetime, velocity
FROM drive 
WHERE trip_id = (
  SELECT trip_id FROM drive WHERE velocity = (SELECT MAX(velocity) FROM drive)
)
ORDER BY datetime
